<H3>
MV Greenpeace / PC 8023
<BR>     
Position: Noon Pos:  22 deg 56 min North and
117 deg 12 min East 

<BR>
June 21st, 1996 
<BR>
Day 36</H3>




<B><P>Hej,

<P>Out at sea again after two good open ships in Hong Kong (about
1800 people).Our noon position today was 22 deg 56 min North and
117 deg 12 min East and ETA Nagasaki 25th of June at 16:00 local
time. Having light wind and following sea and a warm sun.


<P>All the best


<P>Ulf</B>


