<H3>
MV Greenpeace / PC 8023
<BR>     
Position: Noon Pos:  25 deg 30 min North and
121 deg 10 min East 

<BR>
June 22nd, 1996 
<BR>
Day 37</H3>




<B><P>Hej,

<P>Our noon position today was 25 deg 30 min North and
121 deg 10 min East,

<P> Due to a good speed ETA Nagasaki cahanged to 25th of June at 12:00 local
time. Having light southerly wind, following sea and a warm sun.


<P>All the best


<P>Ulf</B>


