signataire of the first anti FNT motion passed by the Senate
on July 1995.<P><HR>
 <P>
Dear friends of Greenpeace,
 <P>
I wish you the best for the <m/v Greenpeace> voyage to
Shangai, whose purpose is to ask China to sign, with the other
Nuclear States, the CTBT, the text of which is under
discussion in Geneva.
 <P>
