Treaty which ends one of the saddest pages of this century,
the nuclear test era. Your mission and the request to meet
Chinese Authorities are peaceful acts representing all those
who wish for an end to nuclear tests.
 <P>
I wish you a most successful journey
 <P>
<I>MoE Edo Ronchi</I>
 


