<H3>GREENPEACE SHIP BOARDED BY CHINESE OFFICIALS</H3>
 

<P>At 1400 hrs (Chinese time) the MV Greenpeace, anchored at the Chang jiang Kou
anchorage inthe approaches to Shangahi  was surrounded by four harbour  boats,
two alongside and two astern of the MV GP.
 
 <P>Over30 Chinese unarmed customs officials  and others came aboard. The Captain
was informed  the ship is in Chinese waters illegally  and will not be allowed
to enter Shanghai.
 
 <P>The Chinese also  took photos and  video. The atmosphere appeared to be
friendly.
 
<P>14.25 The chinese officals have now left the ship. The Captain  has been told
they will be contacted later. 
 
<P>More details later.....


