<A HREF="kerngroepen1.html"><IMG SRC="pagegraphics/kerngroepen.gif" ALT="vrijwilligers"  BORDER=0 WIDTH=98 HEIGHT=45 ALIGN=BOTTOM></A><BR><BR>

