<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~usa/campaigns/biodiversity/tuna.html 193.67.176.1 19970103170821 text/html 13564
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 17:10:59 GMT
