</A> Article VIII(3)

<p> <A HREF = "#textf11">  [11]<A NAME= notef11> </A> 
 
</A> The five tangible steps were: (1) a comprehensive ban on nuclear weapon testing, (2) a complete 
cessation of production of fissionable material for weapon purposes, both in themselves effective non-
proliferation measures, (3) a freeze and a gradual reduction of the stocks of nuclear weapons and the 
means of their delivery, (4) the banning of the use of nuclear weapons and (5) assurance of the security of 
non-nuclear weapon States. See <I>Joint Memorandum</I>, <I>supra</I> note 9.

<p> <A HREF = "#textf12">  [12]<A NAME= notef12> </A> 
 
