</A> Rule 23 provides that:<BR>
The motions indicated below shall have precedence in the   following order over all proposals or other 
motion before the meeting:<BR>
(a)  To suspend the meeting;<BR>
(b)  To adjourn the meeting;<BR>
(c)  To adjourn the debate on the question under discussion;<BR>
(d)  To close the debate on the question under discussion.

