<H2><A HREF="laws82-1.html#Part_V">Part V <BR>
EXCLUSIVE ECONOMIC ZONE  <P>
</H2>
<A HREF ="laws82-1.html#article_55_specific_legal_regime_of">  Article 55  Specific legal regime of the exclusive economic zone</A> <P>
<A HREF ="laws82-1.html#article_56_rights__jurisdiction_and">  Article 56  Rights, jurisdiction and duties of the coastal 
State in the  exclusive economic zone</A> <P>
<A HREF ="laws82-1.html#article_57_breadtof_the_exclusive">  Article 57  Breadth of the exclusive economic zone</A> <P>
