<H1><B><align=left><img src="/icons/isend.gif" border=0 width=36 height=36 alt="Send Mail">  Send a message to a Greenpeace Office</B></H1></head></align=left></center>
<br>
<img WIDTH=560 HEIGHT=29 src="/icons/forest.gif" alt="-------------------------------------------------------------">
<br>
<br><br>
If your browser is properly configured to send email, you 
can use this page to send a message to the Greenpeace office in your country.
If you cannot find your country in the list below, select "Greenpeace Supporter Services"
at the Greenpeace International office in Amsterdam and they will let you know your nearest contact. Just click on the name of the office
you want to send to and your browser will start a message to that office.
<p><b>Select an office to send your message to:</b><br>
<hr>
<a href="mailto:kgallagher@ams.greenpeace.org">Greenpeace Supporter Services</a><br>
