<h3>NOTE: this form can NOT be used by Lynx and AOL (America On Line) browsers!</h3>

<H2>Send a message to the nearest Greenpeace office</H2>
Use this form to send a message to the Greenpeace office in your country.
If you cannot find your country in the list below, select "Supporter Services"
in the Greenpeace International office in Amsterdam, the Netherlands.
<p>
<h3>Please keep these messages short and no file attachments, please!</h3>
<hr>
<FORM METHOD="POST"
ACTION="http://www.greenpeace.org/cgi-bin/form-mailer"> 
