<!--INSERT TEXT HERE>We are currently running three Majordomo e-mail lists to which you can subscribe.  They are:
<br><br><b>ukscience-general</b>
<br>for people interested in receiving info about the UK Science pages - when they are updated, etc.
<br><br><b>ukscience-hormones</b>
<br>for people interested in receiving info about the UK Science hormone disrupting chemical pages - when they are updated, etc.
<br><br><b>ukscience-press</b>
<br>for people interested who want to receive all press releases from the UK Science team.
<p>To subscribe to our lists you should e-mail <a href="mailto:majordomo@xs2.greenpeace.org">majordomo@xs2.greenpeace.org</a> and put the following in the body of your e-mail:
<p>subscribe listname your e-mail address
<p>for example
<p>subscribe ukscience-press john.locke@contract.gov
<p>you should receive a message to say that you are subscribed.  To unsubscribe simply repeat the above process, substituting the work "unsubscribe" for "subscribe"
<hr>
<p>Contact <a href="mailto:helen.wallace@uk.greenpeace.org">helen.wallace@uk.greenpeace.org</a> for questions about the science or
 <a href="mailto:jim@xs2.greenpeace.org">jim@xs2.greenpeace.org</a> for questions about the site
