<BR><a href="mailto:webmaster@shellus.com">e-mail</a> your comments and suggestions (or do it anonymously from the <a href="http://www.idiot.com/~idiot/shell/murdered/ken/Saro-Wiwa/sHELL.html"> idiot site</a>.











